pysandbox is a Python sandbox.

Blocked functions
=================

Functions:

 * Create a file, write into an existing file
 * Import modules or use module attribute not in the whitelist
 * exit()

Protection of the sandbox itself:

 * Read function closure
 * Read function globals


Options
=======

 * open_whitelist: see safe_open()
 * import_whitelist: see safe_import()


Example
=======

Code:

   with Sandbox():
      ... execute unsafe code here ...


See also
========

